@startuml REQ-0011 Humidity Sensing
autonumber

box "System" #LightBlue
  participant "Sensor Driver" as Sensor_Driver
  participant "Controller" as Controller
end box

header
  **REQ-0011: Humidity Sensing**
  //Description:// Read raw humidity from ADC and post sensor data events
  //Acceptance Criteria:// Sensor_ReadHumidity returns valid ADC reading; EVENT:SENSOR_DATA_READY posted
end header

note over Sensor_Driver: aggregate_readings()

Sensor_Driver --> Controller: EVENT:SENSOR_DATA_READY\nSensor_ReadHumidity() → Controller_OnSensorData()

@enduml